However, someone noticed my work at William Hills invited me to interview and I stated my career at my first Agency. Eyal [ee-yaal] means Deer in Hebrew, and for my surname, [Benveniste] from Spanish "Bien veniste" means your arrival was good. It was given to my ancestors by a Spanish king in the medieval. An ideal group would be an intimate, mission-driven, where the team is open minded and ready to continual innovation To meet and connect new people and to be regonize for my work and the my knowladge i provide. Working to solve a problem with a clear 'why' and goal.
